name: This was sorta dumb/a failure - oh well, onto the next
description:
Had a 10k pacing workout planned but the legs were feeling real heavy so I just called it quits which I very shortly after regretted. Maybe I’ll give it another shot tomorrow.
-
Also my watch glitched out, the 2 segments were right after each other & I never slowed down, seeing that happen definitely added discouragement (dumb reason)
Really hoping the gps glitch is just a one-off
